          "ruleId": "d47-io-unsafe-txn",
          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "External IO inside an open write transaction — SuppressedIo performs HTTP Get while a database write is still pending (uncommitted). The external call happens inside an open write transaction — if it blocks or fails the transaction is held open across the network round-trip, and BC's runtime forbids HTTP during a write transaction."
